values:
This week has been crazy man, most good times but also some fucking weird times.
Staying at Kurt's was wicked and I loved hanging out with the guys but now cause of what did happen I've almost lost a friend.
I should have just shut up when I heard 'it was going to be weird', but I couldn't take it. Fuck.

Lost my phone too, fucking cunting pick pockets.

All I wanna do nowadays is go out and get with people, what mistakes.

I felt good last week, I don't feel so great now.
